1207
01:04:58,130 --> 01:05:01,370
That's crazy! De la Cruz
wrote all his own songs.

1208
01:05:01,370 --> 01:05:03,270
You want to tell him
or should I?

1209
01:05:03,270 --> 01:05:05,670
Hector, I never meant
to take credit.

1210
01:05:05,670 --> 01:05:09,240
We made a great team,
but you died...

1211
01:05:09,240 --> 01:05:11,270
