with a toast.

1247
01:06:43,540 --> 01:06:44,810
To our friendship.

1248
01:06:44,810 --> 01:06:49,430
I would move Heaven and Earth
for you, <i>mi amigo. Salud!</i>

1249
01:06:53,750 --> 01:06:55,520
<font color="#138ce9">HECTOR:</font> <i>You walked me
to the train station.</i>

1250
01:06:55,520 --> 01:06:58,390
<i>But I felt
a pain in my stomach.</i>

1251
01:06:58,390 --> 01:07:00,660
<i>I thought it must have been
something I ate.</i>

1252
01:07:00,660 --> 01:07:03,160
Perhaps it was
that <i>chorizo,</i> my friend.

1253
01:07:03,160 --> 01:07:05,710
<font color="#138ce9">HECTOR:</font> <i>Or something I drank.</i>

1254
01:07:09,130 --> 01:07:10,980
<i>I woke up dead.</i>

1255
01:07:12,570 --> 01:07:14,840
You poisoned me.

1256
01:07:14,840 --> 01:07:18,380
